strings: <voice_0x010013EA><se_high>*: (Whoa, who are these people!? Beautiful clothes! Are they friends of the Empire?)
<voice_0x010013EB><se_def>*: (No no! Look at them! They don't look like the old kingdom. Except for the bright clothes)
<voice_0x010013EC><se_def>*: (...he looks like a boy! Yes, he looks weird, but he's still a boy!)
<voice_0x010013EE><se_def>*: (Come on, come on! Calm down! They're innocent, so stop kidding. Call your boss!)
<voice_0x010013F1><se_low>before this: I saw a bear if I remember correctly. Are you in a brighter world?
<voice_0x010013F2><se_low>before this: as i thought It is the wish of the goddess that you come here.
<voice_0x010013F3><se_low>before this: Um... I have something to discuss with you. Maybe you'll come to my house later.
<voice_0x010013F4><se_low>before this: If you agree, you can go out and explore as much as you want.
<voice_0x010013F5><se_low>before this: Wait, my house is the largest room in here, so you know where to find me.
<voice_0x010013F6><se_low>before this: My Bishou platform! We are open again as usual! Remember to be kind to strangers.
<voice_0x010013F7><se_low>before this: Get Free Benefits! You don't need to hide! You can recognize emotions from your facial expressions.
<voice_0x010013F8><se_low>before this: I ask again<:> are you from the world of light?
